text.tspan: Mixing these functions results in a valid-looking but incorrect hash.
They share the same structure but use different constants and operations.

div.p: c // Message Schedule (Lowercase) #define sigma0(x) (ROTR(x, 7) ^ ROTR(x, 18) ^ (x >> 3)) #define sigma1(x) (ROTR(x, 17) ^ ROTR(x, 19) ^ (x >> 10))
